# LetsUpgrade-Blockchain
Day wise Assignments of Blockchain Essentials
Bitcoin is a cryptocurrency which is invented by Satoshi Makamoto on 31st october 2008. it is a kind of moeny which is a peer to peer technology to facilitate payments. it does not have any central bank or administratir. Transactions are verified by all the members who are dealing in it through cryptography and recorded in a public ledger blockchain. 
